  * __aeabi_LC_COLLATE,__aeabi_LC_CTYPE,__aeabi_LC_MONETARY,__aeabi_LC_NUMERIC,
  * __aeabi_LC_TIME,__aeabi_LC_ALL are declared for _AEABI_PORTABILITY_LEVEL macro
